data.description: Welcome to this deceivingly spacious cape style home boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths. On the first floor you will find a large eat in kitchen, spacious living room, 2 bedrooms and full bath. Upstairs you will find a full bath, a large bedroom and a den that can be turned into a 4th bedroom or office space. The full-partial finished basement features a large recreation room, laundry room and another full bath. The backyard is your private oasis with a gazebo, a custom built outdoor family room. The house requires some TLC. This property is a short sale and will require lender approval.
